%N A395702 Number of transitive relations on an n-set that are neither reflexive nor symmetric.
%F A395702 a(n) = A006905(n) - A000798(n) - A000110(n+1) + A000110(n).
%e A395702 For n=2 the a(2)=6 such relations on {1,2} are {(1,2)}, {(2,1)}, {(1,1),(1,2)}, {(1,1),(2,1)}, {(1,2),(2,2)}, {(2,1),(2,2)}. Each is transitive but fails reflexivity (no full diagonal) and fails symmetry (asymmetric off-diagonal entry).
%Y A395702 Cf. A006905, A000798, A000110, A005493, A202534, A394620.
%K A395702 nonn,new
%O A395702 0,3
